title: Star Wars: Princess Leia (Trade Paperback)
description:
When Princess Leia Organa was captured by the Empire, she never betrayed
her convictions — even after the complete destruction of her home world,
Alderaan. When her rescue came, Leia grabbed a blaster and joined the
fight, escaping back to the Rebel Alliance and helping strike the biggest
blow against the Empire — destroying the Death Star! But in the aftermath
of that victory, the question remains: What is a princess without a world?
As Leia grapples with her loss, a new mission leads her to the underground
world of Sullust. The Empire is rounding up fugitive Alderaanians, and
that doesn’t sit well with their Princess! But what can one woman do
against the Galactic Empire? They’re about to find out! Join the galaxy’s
toughest Princess on a quest to save her people and rebuild her life!
Collecting PRINCESS LEIA #1-5.
